														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4675728">
									

<p>Nah. He didn't kill them, 096 did. Otherwise, why would the pacifier be &quot;half crushed&quot;? That detail infers that 096 did something pretty dang violent in there.</p>
<p>One thing I had considered though, was that he may have known the family. Yeah I know, it's a <em>massive</em> stretch, but even as horrific as the scene must have been to witness, I have a hard time believing that the Master Sargeant of a high ranking SCP retrieval task force, skilled even by Foundation standards, would crack over the death of one infant, let alone become so utterly broken over the sight that he'd kill himself.</p>
<p>But if it was his <strong>own</strong> kid, or reminded him of a lost child of his own? Now we're getting somewhere.</p>

